Help, I’m a little new to FIRST and from what I’ve learned I have everything right… I don’t know if its a roboRIO imaging problem. I have a simple arcade drive code that I want to deploy but I can’t connect to the roboRIO. I tried ethernet, radio, usb B… I cant get communications. Don’t mind the messy wiring we had some rookies put it together.

A few things to check:

Do you see the roborio if yoi connect by USB and run the roborio imaging utility ?

Can you connect to the roborio using the web dashboard ? roboRIO Web Dashboard — FIRST Robotics Competition documentation

Is the team number set correctly in VSCode ?

What is the error message you get when you try to deploy code by
USB?
